attributes.visual_style: Spaghetti Western meets cinematic realism — lots of sun-faded textures, horses, saloons, and wooden storefronts.
attributes.tone: Dusty, tense, morally ambiguous — a place where legends and criminals blur.
attributes.time: Circa 1885 — just before modern law took full hold
attributes.narrative_context: This is where Buckley grew up. It's also where he first met Seamus as kids. The lasso was buried just outside town. Many timelines flicker back to Dodge as a convergence point.
attributes.notes: Dodge City has a strange gravitational pull in time — things always seem to return here. There's something under the saloon no one talks about. Seamus hates the dust but secretly feels at home here.
